.html&#34;&gt;Cara Membuat Cron Job Menggunakan webcron.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;  &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;div&gt;   &lt;h3&gt;Cara Install Bot Auto Reaction Facebook Lewat Termux&lt;/h3&gt;   &lt;ol&gt;    &lt;li&gt;     &lt;a href=&#34;https://pastebin.com/b0Q8JkH5&#34; class=&#34;w3-text-green&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferer nofollow&#34;&gt;Download Scriptnya&lt;/a&gt;. simpan dengan nama bot.php     &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Taruh file bot.php ke /sdcard&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Edit bot.php. masukkan user dan password facebooknya&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Lalu masuk ke termux. dan ketik kode dibawah ini&lt;/li&gt;   &lt;/ol&gt;   &lt;pre&gt;&lt;br&gt;   cd $HOME&lt;br&gt;   apt update &amp;amp;&amp;amp; apt upgrade&lt;br&gt;   apt install vim php -y&lt;br&gt;   export VISUAL=vim&lt;br&gt;   export EDITOR=vim&lt;br&gt;   echo &#39;#!/bin/sh&#39; &amp;gt; autoloader&lt;br&gt;   echo &#34;cd /sdcard&#34; &amp;gt;&amp;gt; autoloader&lt;br&gt;   echo &#34;php -f bot.php&#34; &amp;gt;&amp;gt; autoloader&lt;br&gt;   chmod 777 autoloader&lt;br&gt;   cat autoloader&lt;br&gt;   user=$(whoami)&lt;br&gt;   echo &#34;*/1 * * * * sh $HOME/autoloader&#34; &amp;gt; cron&lt;br&gt;   crontab -c $user cron&lt;br&gt;   crontab -r&lt;br&gt;   crontab cron&lt;br&gt;   clear &amp;amp;&amp;amp; crontab -l &amp;amp;&amp;amp; cat autoloader&lt;br&gt;   crond stop &amp;amp;&amp;amp; crond start&lt;br&gt;   &lt;/pre&gt;   Hasilnya akan keluar di /sdcard/results.html. seperti dibawah ini.     &lt;div class=&#34;w3-center&#34;&gt;    &lt;img src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/dimaslanjaka/image/fetch/https://imgdb.net/images/4306.jpg&#34; class=&#34;w3-center&#34; width=&#34;300&#34; height=&#34;300&#34;&gt;    &lt;/div&gt;  &lt;/div&gt; &lt;iframe width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;294&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/-ImhbXQEdPI?&amp;amp;theme=dark&amp;amp;autohide=2&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;font-size: 0.8em&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https:/